source.name: Top 100 Recipients of Federal Contract Awards for FY 2008
source.description: The contracts database is compiled from the FPDS-NG system.  Note: The numbers in this table can change after each data load. Transactions included in a data load can impact numbers for the current and previous fiscal years.  The data housed on USASpending.gov is provided by Federal agencies.  USASpending.gov is continuously developing ways to measure and improve the quality of the data.
